    Process raw data

    process_text.Rd

    Process raw data

    Usage

    process_text(raw_data, fct = FALSE)

    Arguments

    raw_data

    raw dataset

    fct

    include factors?

    Value

    data with standardized names, lowercase text, etc.

    Examples
